data.description: Welcome to this rancher located in the borough of Middletown.  This home is located in a quite section of town on a corner lot with a fenced in yard, 2 storage sheds and off street parking for 2-3 vehicles. The home has 3 bedrooms with the master having double closets  and a full bathroom.  The kitchen has full appliances with the refrigerator only being 1 year old.  You will also find a washer & dryer on the main lever that are only 2 years old. On the back is a spacious family room with sliding glass doors that lead out onto a nice big deck perfect for outdoor living and entertaining. The roof was replaced in 2020 along with the water heater carpeting, water softner, windows, ceiling fans and a fence.  A firepit was added to the front yard to enjoy those crisp evenings outside.  Great fenced in yard for pets and kids.  Come check us out.
